nodes.text: A squid-like bounty hunter, along with the bounty hunter 4-LOM and another hunter, once stowed away aboard the personal starship of the fellow bounty hunter Boba Fett, Slave I, in 3.5 ABY in order to attempt to steal the captured carbonite-frozen Han Solo from Fett and the hefty reward that went with it. However, Fett realized there were intruders aboard and killed the squid-like hunter and the other hunter, while neutralizing 4-LOM.
